xt]Several meticulously designed feature walls in the flagship brighten up the ambiance, injecting a fun, adorable personality into this cosy setting. Aimed to brighten everybody&#8217;s day, stepping into this DurianBB flagship brings about a happy, cheery mood. Furthermore, in line with the brand&#8217;s motto to deliver happiness, the flagship includes two claw machines filled with DurianBB premium plushies that are up for grabs!<\/p>\n<p>Another notable highlight in the flagship is none other than the custom-built display counter, featuring gourmet cakes, beverages, fresh pulps and soft-serve &#8211; ALL made with the freshest durian flesh.[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]Set in a corner is a dedicated tiered seating section where durian fans can mingle with one another and watch interactive videos prepared by the team. The seats are designed to have close proximity where fellow great minds come together and share their love for durian.[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;4845&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;4841&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Coming to Shanghai? Visit Us at:&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|font_size:20|text_align:center|color:%238e8e8e&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Opening Hours\uff1a10:00-22:00<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Shop No.\uff1a\u73af\u5b87\u835fB009<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Tel No.\uff1a17717902976<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.durianbb.com.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.durianbb.com.cn<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;4842&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_